WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:25.000
Photo Finish by Polly Sweetman

00:25.000 --> 00:28.000
Lisa works at Black and Sons

00:28.000 --> 00:32.000
Black and Sons is a large company

00:32.000 --> 00:36.000
Lisa works in the accounts department

00:36.000 --> 00:39.000
The work is very important

00:39.000 --> 00:44.000
but it is not very exciting

00:44.000 --> 00:48.000
Your holiday is next week Lisa, are you excited?

00:48.000 --> 00:52.000
Oh yes, I'm going to go with Alice

00:52.000 --> 00:55.000
We're going to go to Greece

00:55.000 --> 00:57.000
It will be fun

00:57.000 --> 01:02.000
Perhaps something exciting will happen

01:02.000 --> 01:05.000
Alice is Lisa's friend

01:05.000 --> 01:09.000
Alice works for Black and Sons too

01:09.000 --> 01:12.000
She works in the marketing department

01:12.000 --> 01:15.000
Alice is an artist

01:15.000 --> 01:20.000
She designs advertisements for Black and Sons

01:21.000 --> 01:24.000
I want to work with Alice

01:24.000 --> 01:28.000
I want to work in the marketing department

01:28.000 --> 01:33.000
The marketing department is always busy

01:33.000 --> 01:37.000
Everybody is very friendly

01:37.000 --> 01:40.000
They have exciting jobs

01:44.000 --> 01:46.000
Alice phones Lisa

01:46.000 --> 01:49.000
They are going to get their passports today

01:49.000 --> 01:52.000
They must go to the post office

01:52.000 --> 01:54.000
Hi Lisa

01:54.000 --> 01:55.000
Hello Alice

01:55.000 --> 01:57.000
Let's meet at lunchtime

01:57.000 --> 02:01.000
Then we can get our passports for our holiday

02:01.000 --> 02:07.000
Okay, I'll meet you outside the office at 1230

02:08.000 --> 02:12.000
Lisa and Alice are in the post office

02:12.000 --> 02:17.000
The assistant gives the passport forms to the two friends

02:17.000 --> 02:20.000
Please fill in these forms

02:20.000 --> 02:23.000
Where are your passport photos?

02:23.000 --> 02:26.000
Here are my photos

02:26.000 --> 02:28.000
Oh no!

02:28.000 --> 02:32.000
My photos aren't in my bag

02:33.000 --> 02:37.000
My photos are at home

02:37.000 --> 02:43.000
Lisa, you must go to the photo booth in the old bus station

02:43.000 --> 02:46.000
You can get your photos there

02:46.000 --> 02:49.000
Oh no!

02:49.000 --> 02:52.000
I hate the old bus station

02:52.000 --> 02:55.000
I don't want to go there

02:55.000 --> 02:59.000
But you must get the photos today

03:00.000 --> 03:03.000
Listen, I can fill in the forms

03:03.000 --> 03:06.000
Go to the bus station Lisa

03:06.000 --> 03:09.000
Go and get your photos

03:09.000 --> 03:13.000
I'll wait for you here

03:16.000 --> 03:19.000
Nobody goes to the bus station now

03:19.000 --> 03:23.000
There is a new bus station in the centre of town

03:23.000 --> 03:27.000
The old bus station is empty and dark

03:28.000 --> 03:31.000
Lisa walks quickly

03:31.000 --> 03:35.000
Her shoes make a loud noise on the ground

03:35.000 --> 03:39.000
Then she sees the photo booth

03:39.000 --> 03:43.000
There is nobody in the photo booth

03:43.000 --> 03:46.000
Lisa is happy

03:46.000 --> 03:50.000
She can get her photos quickly

03:50.000 --> 03:54.000
Lisa goes into the photo booth

03:55.000 --> 03:58.000
She puts her money into the machine

03:58.000 --> 04:01.000
She closes the little curtain

04:01.000 --> 04:03.000
She sits down

04:03.000 --> 04:06.000
She waits

04:06.000 --> 04:08.000
Flash

04:08.000 --> 04:11.000
The camera is very quick

04:11.000 --> 04:12.000
Flash

04:12.000 --> 04:14.000
Flash

04:14.000 --> 04:16.000
Flash

04:16.000 --> 04:21.000
Now Lisa can get her passport today

04:21.000 --> 04:24.000
Lisa goes outside the photo booth

04:24.000 --> 04:30.000
Her photos will come out of a slot in the machine

04:30.000 --> 04:32.000
Lisa, here's a noise

04:32.000 --> 04:36.000
Some photos are coming out of the slot

04:36.000 --> 04:38.000
Are they her photos?

04:38.000 --> 04:41.000
No, it is too soon

04:41.000 --> 04:45.000
Lisa's photos can't be ready

04:45.000 --> 04:47.000
But who is in the photos?

04:47.000 --> 04:50.000
There is nobody in the bus station

04:50.000 --> 04:54.000
Nobody else is waiting for photos

04:54.000 --> 04:58.000
Lisa is alone

04:58.000 --> 05:02.000
Lisa takes the photos out of the slot

05:02.000 --> 05:06.000
There is a man in the pictures

05:06.000 --> 05:09.000
But something is wrong

05:09.000 --> 05:12.000
She is frightened

05:12.000 --> 05:16.000
The four photos show a murder

05:16.000 --> 05:19.000
There is a man in the first photo

05:19.000 --> 05:22.000
He is very large

05:22.000 --> 05:27.000
He is wearing a black coat and a red scarf

05:27.000 --> 05:30.000
The man is sitting in the photo booth

05:30.000 --> 05:33.000
He is smiling

05:33.000 --> 05:36.000
It is not a nice smile

05:36.000 --> 05:40.000
It is a cruel smile

05:40.000 --> 05:43.000
The man is in the second photo

05:43.000 --> 05:46.000
The man is looking to the right

05:46.000 --> 05:50.000
He is afraid

05:50.000 --> 05:54.000
Something is happening in the third photo

05:54.000 --> 05:58.000
Somebody is holding the man's scarf

05:58.000 --> 06:03.000
Somebody is holding the man's scarf very tightly

06:03.000 --> 06:09.000
The large man is pulling at his scarf

06:09.000 --> 06:12.000
There is no man in the fourth photo

06:12.000 --> 06:15.000
There are two hands

06:15.000 --> 06:19.000
The hands are holding the red scarf

06:19.000 --> 06:23.000
There is a ring on one of the hands

06:23.000 --> 06:26.000
It is a strange ring

06:26.000 --> 06:30.000
There is a snake on the ring

06:30.000 --> 06:33.000
There is a tattoo on the other hand

06:33.000 --> 06:37.000
It is a tattoo of a bird

06:37.000 --> 06:42.000
The hands are the murderer's hands

06:42.000 --> 06:46.000
Now Lisa is very frightened

06:46.000 --> 06:51.000
The man with the red scarf is dead

06:51.000 --> 06:54.000
But where is his body?

06:54.000 --> 06:57.000
Where is the murderer?

06:57.000 --> 07:01.000
Is the murderer in the bus station?

07:01.000 --> 07:05.000
The photos show the murder

07:05.000 --> 07:10.000
The murderer knows about the photos

07:10.000 --> 07:15.000
The murderer will come back to the photo booth

07:15.000 --> 07:19.000
He will want the photos

07:19.000 --> 07:24.000
I'm in danger

07:27.000 --> 07:31.000
Lisa and Alice are at the police station

07:31.000 --> 07:35.000
They are telling their story to the police

07:35.000 --> 07:39.000
They are showing the photos to a detective

07:39.000 --> 07:42.000
She is very interested

07:42.000 --> 07:45.000
The detective has a plan

07:45.000 --> 07:48.000
I know the man in the photos

07:48.000 --> 07:51.000
He is a criminal

07:51.000 --> 07:53.000
Now he is dead

07:53.000 --> 07:56.000
But we can catch his murderer

07:56.000 --> 08:00.000
The murderer will go back to the photo booth

08:00.000 --> 08:03.000
He will want his photos

08:03.000 --> 08:06.000
But he will find your photos Lisa

08:06.000 --> 08:09.000
He will look for you

08:09.000 --> 08:12.000
You can help us Lisa

08:18.000 --> 08:21.000
Lisa is in the bus station

08:21.000 --> 08:25.000
She is walking towards the photo booth

08:25.000 --> 08:29.000
She is going to get her photos

08:29.000 --> 08:32.000
The police are in the bus station

08:32.000 --> 08:34.000
They are hiding

08:34.000 --> 08:37.000
They are watching Lisa

08:37.000 --> 08:41.000
They are waiting for the murderer

08:41.000 --> 08:44.000
Lisa walks slowly

08:44.000 --> 08:49.000
She is very frightened

08:51.000 --> 08:54.000
A man is standing by the photo booth

08:54.000 --> 08:57.000
He is young and handsome

08:57.000 --> 09:01.000
Is this the murderer?

09:01.000 --> 09:04.000
The man sees Lisa

09:04.000 --> 09:06.000
He smiles at her

09:06.000 --> 09:09.000
He has a nice smile

09:09.000 --> 09:12.000
He is holding some photos

09:12.000 --> 09:16.000
Lisa sees his hands

09:16.000 --> 09:19.000
She sees the snake ring

09:19.000 --> 09:23.000
She sees the bird tattoo

09:23.000 --> 09:26.000
The police catch the murderer

09:26.000 --> 09:29.000
The detective is pleased

09:29.000 --> 09:32.000
Lisa is safe

09:32.000 --> 09:35.000
Thank you for your help Lisa

09:35.000 --> 09:37.000
Well done Lisa

09:37.000 --> 09:40.000
It is exciting to catch criminals

09:40.000 --> 09:43.000
Exciting? No

09:43.000 --> 09:45.000
It is very frightening

09:45.000 --> 09:48.000
But everything is ok now

09:48.000 --> 09:50.000
We are going on holiday

09:50.000 --> 09:52.000
It will be fun

09:52.000 --> 09:53.000
Yes

09:53.000 --> 09:56.000
Perhaps something exciting will happen

09:59.000 --> 10:02.000
Thank you

10:02.000 --> 10:05.000
Lisa

